# NEWS

## v0.1.2 (Latest)
 * Fixed FAO Tier1 indices to correctly return yearly data instead of daily
 * Changed parameter name from `t2m` to `tm` to match FAO naming conventions directly
 * Removed unused `input.arg.list` parameter
 * Enhanced documentation for `index.arg.list` with comprehensive parameter descriptions
 * Updated parameter documentation for `tm` naming convention
 * Updated README with detailed usage examples and index-specific arguments guide

## v0.1.1 (27 Oct 2025)
 * Fixed critical bugs in FAO Tier1 index calculations
 * Enhanced error handling and edge case management
 * Improved grid compatibility and robustness
 * Optimized parallel processing and grid operations

## v0.0.1 (20 Oct 2025)
 * Initial implementation of agroindexGrid function
 * Added FAO Tier1 indices (11 indices)
 * Added FAO Agronomic Season indices (12 indices)
 * Added CDI and CEI stress indices
 * Basic error handling and validation

## v0.0.0 (13 Oct 2025)
 * Package release